es/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓醒未呀？<br />\n<br />\n就係睇唔過眼你為咗快，咩狗屎垃圾&quot;假情報&quot;﹑&quot;個人漢化&quot;﹑&quot;二三手漢化&quot;都開嚟霸位，<br />\n要鬥早咁我學你早一年開都得啦，夠早啦係咪個個都要入我po呀？<br />\n人拳超人po就最好，早期呢度根本就輪流開po，邊個見有出就開帖討論，樂也融融，<br />\n你明明就冇睇又扮有睇，見多人回就搶po.<br />\n你開中英日韓就各一個po，自己重複在先，就屌人重複po，一見唔夠搶就開多個，無所不用其極。goodest logic<br />\n<br />\n漫畫黨班友就最撚善良, 由得你，次次見你開左po就唔同你爭，廢時分散人流，結果就個個直入你個po。<br />\n寧願硬食你啲屎，&quot;假情報&quot;﹑&quot;個人漢化&quot;﹑&quot;二三手漢化&quot;﹑中英日韓就各一個po. 都只係屌一兩句。<br />\n我就唔會咁犯賤睬你都傻，長痛不如短痛，話知你喺度賴屎賴尿"},{"pid":"1da5427f2958fd1a24f4af4035edb27afe7f5923","tid":547501,"uid":39020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"一拳超人 1359 韓文"},{"pid":"c5f996c9e5fb5356774a368ff4a1d55114c733f5","tid":547501,"uid":35373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個開先喎 等我黎呢到傾先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個開先</blockquote><br />\n井妹真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n扑左井狗，睇唔到佢po"},{"pid":"1418f3083dcb09fb2eca775cb6a1ffdbb4b97d4a","tid":547501,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:39:49.000Z","msg":"又block人又走入嚟負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7812795a0f5015ad2639729e5a659a9f86421dc","tid":547501,"uid":1130,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/02/134603_7f293ac65aa7637fd0e4be427c1d92d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F134603_7f293ac65aa7637fd0e4be427c1d92d7.png&h=3bf5d792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度得一個post<br />\n<br />\n但係幅圖個user 兩個post<br />\n<br />\n咁重覆post嘅定義係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c90538dd16a5c5224d072fff6ffcf718f33b